<item>
            <title>[LU-6036] Interop recovery-small test_18a: test_18a failed with 3 </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6036</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/41591dca-7fb3-11e4-a9c0-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/41591dca-7fb3-11e4-a9c0-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_18a failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;test_18a failed with 3
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;it looks this part of code failed&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;local osc2dev=`lctl get_param -n devices | grep ${ost2_svc}-osc- | egrep -v &apos;MDT&apos; | awk &apos;{print $1}&apos;`
    $LCTL --device $osc2dev deactivate || return 3
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: recovery-small 18a&lt;/p&gt;</description>
